snippet.title: CRUSH - Official Teaser
snippet.description:
This is the official teaser to our Steam Greenlight game CRUSH, an oldschool Shoot´em up.
You can download the free demoversion (including the first level) here: 
http://vis-games.de.www254.your-server.de/vis-games/downloads/Crush-DemoVersion_VIS-Games2016.zip

If you like the game, support us on Steam Greenlight:

http://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=817590452&searchtext=Crush
